h4 Params

p The sparkline inherits all params from TimePlot, with the following differences:

table.params-table
    tr
        td param
        td type
        td default
        td description
    tr
        td fade
        td Boolean
        td true
        td Makes the plot line fade to the left
    tr
        td endpoint
        td Boolean
        td true
        td Draws a circle at the end
    

//
h4 Update

p.
    Call the update method with the new value to update the control

code
    | Subtle.GaugeHistoric.update(value, time = "")

p.
    Here the time can be specified as an ISO string (YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS) or as a javascript Date
    (the default value, an empty string, means that the value passed corresponds to the present time).


